            <div class="title">
                Socialised Industries (Questions To Ministers)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1948-02-04/debates/ecb1d506-fa82-4434-8c86-f209bbf0bbda/PersonalIncomesCostsAndPrices" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
